MBOMBELA &#8211; A driver of a sedan was killed instantly during a head on collision with a fuel tanker this morning. Department of Safety and Security spokesman Mr Joseph Mabuza said at around 00:20 collided head on with the tanker truck on the N4 bypass Road towards Karino about one kilometer from the split.The vehicle was travelling from the direction of Ngodwana and the truck from the opposite direction. The truck driver was transported to hospital with injuries.Police are investigating the accident.